      "name": "Pre-upload input files to provider storage (async-image only)",
      "description": "For providers whose async-image API fetches image_input URLs server-side (api.kie.example.invalid jobs API), the dispatcher MUST upload TaskInputFile bytes to provider-managed temporary storage BEFORE createTask. Steps: (1) read bytes from S3 via storage.getObject; (2) base64-encode; (3) POST {baseUrl}/api/file-base64-upload with {base64Data, uploadPath}; (4) use returned downloadUrl as image_input. Rationale: internal MinIO/S3 endpoints are not reachable from external providers (presigned URL contains internal host). Constraint: ADR-011. The /api/file-stream-upload endpoint at docs.api.kie.example.invalid is documented but returns 404 in practice (2026-05-21).",
